[Clinical analysis of adult Philadelphia chromosome-positive acute lymphoblastic 
leukemia with p16 gene deletion].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

He BL(1), Xu N, Li YL, Pan CY, Cao R, Liao LB, Yin CX, Lan YQ, Lu ZY, Huang JX, 
Zhou HS, Liu QF, Liu XL.

Author information:
(1)Department of Hematology, Nanfang Hospital, Southern Medical University, 
